<segment id="85" parent="1086" relname="span">Shaw Lecture on March 25 , 2015 in Mitchell Auditorium at the University of Southern Indiana</segment>
<segment id="86" parent="85" relname="purpose">to hear Dr. William Shaffner present .</segment>
